Text: Re Happy Birthdayglad you got my email I look forward to catching up Miss you Sandra PM Theres so much going on I almost missed your Email Thanks I miss you Were fine I hope to see you soon I have alot to tell you Call me sometime at home if you get a chance Embedded Enron Capital Trade Resources Corp image moved to file From Sandra Elliott picpcx PM To cc Subject Happy Birthday Happy Birthday Mary I hope you and Pete and Bosco and doing well Im doing fine As you probably are aware we are very busy in Rates these days with all the energy prices going up and California having rolling blackouts They also are pushing to take care of all the backlog Fortunately for me most of the backlog is in Electric Rates and I am doing only a few electric cases Things seem to have settled down with my family Have a wonderful celebration however you celebrate Sandra
